snippet.title: Super Luigi 64 | Beta Luigi 64 | L is real 64 | ROM hack mod Release Trailer and Download
snippet.description:
Super Luigi 64 is finally here. Sure it's been difficult, but it's all worth it.
Link: https://www.mediafire.com/file/l1xaiawsygy6jdq/Super_Luigi_64_V2.0.zip/file
Link for pink screen version: https://www.mediafire.com/file/q3j218fpldf7ri2/Super_Luigi_64_Pink_Screen_patches.zip/file
Discord: https://discord.gg/YjwxHd3y
Songs used:
Don't stop me now (Instrumental): https://youtu.be/G962z-4OL9E
Classic TPIR cues 1972: https://youtu.be/F3iF9dRF8AQ
L IS REAL 2401: https://youtu.be/TXuhzW373YA
Voice clips (mostly) by Andrat.
